{"tid":648642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"報道指美國將進一步限制中國投資美國公司　可能將相關法案附加入《美國國防授權法》","createTime":"2018-04-30T23:18:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T02:08:31.000Z","uid":147314,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b3da8cce599a440399350e8fa12e70a8cbfd6a6d","tid":648642,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T23:18:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1005821&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1005821%26csid%3D261_341&d=W5QmFJY5hwVuk6%2FN%2FfnFXI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=66838b3b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1005821&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<br />\n報道指美財政部官員與商界商討限制中國投資法案<br />\n<br />\n外電引述三名消息人士透露，美國財政部官員周一與約10個行業團體會面，商討國會正審議收緊審查外國投資的法案，從而限制中國獲取美國尖端技術。法案將擴大美國外國投資委員會的權力，進一步限制中國投資美國公司。報道又指，會議亦可能討論將相關法案，附加入《美國國防授權法》中。財政部發言人拒絕回應報道。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1394012-20180501.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1394012-20180501.htm&d=W5QmFJY5hwVuk6%2FN%2FfnFXI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=2b594e85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1394012-20180501.htm&h=cf6f79f2\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1394012-20180501.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n報道稱美官員與商界討論收緊限制擬阻中國投資高新科技<br />\n<br />\n外電報道，美國財政部官員與10個工商組織會晤，討論收緊審核外資投資的法案，相信是要限制中國資本收購美國高新科技產業。<br />\n<br />\n報道指出，美國財政部官員支持法案，法案現時在參議院審議，相信會擴大外國在美投資委員會所涉及的範圍。<br />\n<br />\n分析相信，若果美國限制中國投資，可能會導致中國採取報復，同樣會採取措施限制美國資金到中國投資。"},{"pid":"35ab4046f95625b9b2966413797a7cd0bae842bf","tid":648642,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T23:21:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05db47cf0a9b3bbaf034a87b8384adb98b43da2a","tid":648642,"uid":104699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T23:27:24.000Z","msg":"唔俾人偷技術人地點玩啊"},{"pid":"3a36c7319f236c54b52c297c27d9dac70bebbffe","tid":648642,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T23:32:18.000Z","msg":"美國不知幾想你鎖國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf6991270529bf6c56ea7c0b7e733d3064d5b0d0","tid":648642,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T00:29:51.000Z","msg":"贏國又贏"},{"pid":"d8baa3d3e5c233175315e59998527413ebf939b2","tid":648642,"uid":125809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T01:44:02.000Z","msg":"In Trump WE trust<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb8698bfbbe8a4fe7e4ba204c883ff8ac76259b9","tid":648642,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T01:50:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cfb772c933011c3f5beb9da99c37b0854fe563d","tid":648642,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T02:03:38.000Z","msg":"美國害怕被中國科技超前，慌忙鎖國！中國又贏了！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c114557fbedb00f244b3db291d3fab032a3044fc","tid":648642,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T02:05:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嚇到美國怕怕"},{"pid":"ef4480b5214175919bffe7f5f0f64a7971843a8b","tid":648642,"uid":129664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T02:08:31.000Z","msg":"中唔知乜嘢家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}